**Rendering Detail — Visual Effects Specification**

**Background Layer:**
```
// Subtle center radial glow
const gradient = ctx.createRadialGradient(cx, cy, 0, cx, cy, Math.max(w, h) * 0.45);
gradient.addColorStop(0, 'rgba(97, 0, 223, 0.06)');  // #6100DF at 6%
gradient.addColorStop(0.5, 'rgba(97, 0, 223, 0.02)');
gradient.addColorStop(1, 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)');
ctx.fillStyle = gradient;
ctx.fillRect(0, 0, w, h);
```

**Connection Lines:**
```
// For each connection between nodeA and nodeB:
const avgBrightness = (nodeA.brightness + nodeB.brightness) / 2;
ctx.strokeStyle = `rgba(139, 92, 246, ${0.04 + avgBrightness * 0.12})`;
ctx.lineWidth = 0.5 + avgBrightness * 0.5;
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.moveTo(nodeA.x, nodeA.y);
ctx.lineTo(nodeB.x, nodeB.y);
ctx.stroke();
```

**Network Nodes:**
```
// For each node:
ctx.globalCompositeOperation = 'lighter';
// Outer glow
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(node.x, node.y, node.radius * 5, 0, TAU);
ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(97, 0, 223, ${0.015 * node.brightness})`;
ctx.fill();
// Middle glow
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(node.x, node.y, node.radius * 2.5, 0, TAU);
ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(139, 92, 246, ${0.06 * node.brightness})`;
ctx.fill();
// Core
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(node.x, node.y, node.radius, 0, TAU);
ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(139, 92, 246, ${0.3 + 0.7 * node.brightness})`;
ctx.fill();
ctx.globalCompositeOperation = 'source-over';
```

**Query Text Rendering:**
```
ctx.font = '13px "Hikasami", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif';
ctx.textBaseline = 'middle';
// Only render characters up to charIndex
const visibleText = query.text.substring(0, query.charIndex);
ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(255, 255, 255, ${query.opacity * 0.85})`;
// Shadow for glow effect
ctx.shadowColor = 'rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5)';
ctx.shadowBlur = 8;
ctx.fillText(visibleText, query.x, query.y);
ctx.shadowBlur = 0;
// Blinking cursor during typing
if (query.phase === 'typing' && Math.sin(time * 6) > 0) {
  const cursorX = query.x + ctx.measureText(visibleText).width + 2;
  ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.8)`;
  ctx.fillRect(cursorX, query.y - 7, 1.5, 14);
}
```

**Brand Result Rendering:**
```
// Cited brand
ctx.font = 'bold 14px "Hikasami", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif';
ctx.textBaseline = 'middle';
if (brand.cited) {
  // Halo ring
  ctx.globalCompositeOperation = 'lighter';
  ctx.beginPath();
  ctx.arc(brand.x - 10, brand.y, brand.haloRadius, 0, TAU);
  ctx.strokeStyle = `rgba(139, 92, 246, ${0.2 * brand.opacity * (0.7 + 0.3 * Math.sin(time * 2.5))})`;
  ctx.lineWidth = 1.5;
  ctx.stroke();
  // Soft bloom behind text
  ctx.beginPath();
  ctx.arc(brand.x + textWidth/2, brand.y, textWidth * 0.6, 0, TAU);
  ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(97, 0, 223, ${0.04 * brand.opacity})`;
  ctx.fill();
  ctx.globalCompositeOperation = 'source-over';
  // Text
  ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(168, 85, 247, ${brand.opacity})`;  // #A855F7
  ctx.shadowColor = 'rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6)';
  ctx.shadowBlur = 12;
  ctx.fillText(brand.name, brand.x, brand.y);
  ctx.shadowBlur = 0;
  // Small checkmark
  ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(34, 197, 94, ${brand.opacity * 0.8})`;
  ctx.font = '10px system-ui';
  ctx.fillText('✓', brand.x + textWidth + 6, brand.y);
} else {
  // Ghost brand
  ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(255, 255, 255, ${brand.opacity * 0.2})`;
  ctx.font = '13px "Hikasami", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif';
  ctx.fillText(brand.name, brand.x, brand.y);
  // Strikethrough effect
  ctx.strokeStyle = `rgba(239, 68, 68, ${brand.opacity * 0.15})`;
  ctx.lineWidth = 0.8;
  ctx.beginPath();
  ctx.moveTo(brand.x - 4, brand.y);
  ctx.lineTo(brand.x + textWidth + 4, brand.y);
  ctx.stroke();
}
```

**Energy Pulse Rendering:**
```
// Interpolate position along connection
const nodeA = nodes[pulse.fromNode];
const nodeB = nodes[pulse.toNode];
const px = nodeA.x + (nodeB.x - nodeA.x) * pulse.progress;
const py = nodeA.y + (nodeB.y - nodeA.y) * pulse.progress;
// Draw pulse dot
ctx.globalCompositeOperation = 'lighter';
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(px, py, pulse.size * 3, 0, TAU);
ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(139, 92, 246, ${0.1 * pulse.opacity})`;
ctx.fill();
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(px, py, pulse.size, 0, TAU);
ctx.fillStyle = `rgba(200, 180, 255, ${0.8 * pulse.opacity})`;
ctx.fill();
ctx.globalCompositeOperation = 'source-over';
```

**Static Frame for Reduced Motion:**
- Render all nodes at brightness 0.5
- Render all connections at base opacity
- No particles, no queries, no brands animating
- Just the static neural network constellation — beautiful and still
- Add 3 brand names on the right (pre-placed, 2 cited, 1 ghost)
- Add 2 query texts on the left (fully typed, no dissolving)

This completes the full visual specification. The implementation is deterministic from this design.
